Enter this location at 333 O\'Keefe Ave. This is the P146 lot, operated by Premium Parking. It is located on the west/left-hand side of O\'Keefe Ave. (a one-way street) between Perdido St. and Union St. The entrance is marked by a red \'P\' sign with white lettering.
By clicking create account you agree to RunParking Terms of Use and Privacy Policy
● Height Restriction: 6\' 8\" \n● This facility does not accept luxury and/or exotic vehicles
Make sure your license plate matches the plate on your Parking Pass.

You may park anywhere that doesn\'t say “Reserved”, have a person’s name, a business name, or any other special signage or messaging on the actual space. Failure to do so will result in a ticket, tow, or immobilization.
Simply leave when you\'re ready to go!
